Package: uccdf
Type: Package
Title: Minimal Consensus Clustering for Tabular Data Frames
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Dai",
      family = "Dai",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "daik54015@gmail.com"
    )
  )
Description: Provides a minimal consensus clustering workflow for tabular
    data frames. The package validates input, infers a simple schema,
    builds distance and latent representations, aggregates clustering runs
    across resamples, selects a supported cluster count, and returns
    sample-level assignments with confidence summaries.
